1).List the details of Students who are all studying in 2nd sem MCA. 
  
  select usn,name 
   from student,branch
   where student.Branch_id=branch.Branch_id 
   and Branch_name="MCA"
   order by Name;
OR
select usn,name 
from student s,branch b
where s.Branch_id=b.Branch_id 
and Branch_name="MCA";

