5) Display the student details who borrowed more than two books.
    select *
    from student
    where usn in(select Usn from borrow 
    group by Usn having count(Usn)>=2);
+------------+---------+---------+-----------+------+
| Usn        | Name    | Address | Branch_id | Sem  |
